items.title: Could Buying Visa Stock Today Set You Up for Life?
items.description: Favorable tailwinds support Visa's durable double-digit growth, which is set to continue in the years ahead.  The company's massive ecosystem, consisting of cards and merchants, creates a powerful network effect.  In the past, Visa (NYSE: V) has done just that.

items.title: Is the Artificial Intelligence Boost Fading for This Top Tech Stock?
items.author: Eric Volkman
items.description: Workday, a financial services company, reported strong Q1 results, but its guidance disappointed investors who expected higher growth rates due to the company's focus on artificial intelligence (AI) technology. Despite the market's reaction, Workday's AI offerings are gaining traction with its clients, and analysts predict continued growth for the company.
